title: You are responsible for maintaining the security of your account and for the activities on your account
quoteText:
You must keep your account and passwords confidential and not authorize any third party to access or use the Service on your behalf, unless we provide an approved mechanism for such use.
Keybase will not be liable for any loss or damage arising from any unauthorized use of your accounts
